---
title: Chicken & Zucchini Rigatoni Rosa with Cream Cheese, Parm & Arugula Salad
description: Fun fact: “Rosa” means “pink” in Italian. For our chefs’ version of rigatoni rosa, you’ll make a homemade pink sauce with a savory sausage base and a sprinkle of chili flakes (for a little heat!). Toss that with rigatoni and sautéed zucchini, then sprinkle Parmesan all over and serve with a lemony arugula salad. We promise: you’ll be blushing from all the compliments you receive on this meal.
